01:46:38.984 --> 01:46:41.179
Does he expect you?

01:46:41.253 --> 01:46:44.450
Do you have keys to the apartment?

01:46:44.523 --> 01:46:47.788
Is there a code, a way of knocking,
so he knows it's you?

01:47:35.874 --> 01:47:37.273
Alpha team.

01:47:37.343 --> 01:47:40.938
<i>- Final position. We're ready to go.
- Be careful.</i>

01:48:27.993 --> 01:48:31.156
What up? Move! Fuck.

01:48:36.502 --> 01:48:38.333
Shit.

01:48:39.772 --> 01:48:41.763
Alpha team. Man down.

01:48:43.008 --> 01:48:45.135
I told you.

01:48:49.014 --> 01:48:51.778
- Bring me everyone.
- What do you mean, "everyone"?

01:48:51.850 --> 01:48:54.318
Everyone!

01:49:48.140 --> 01:49:50.074
Take this.

01:49:55.914 --> 01:49:59.008
Go take a look.

01:50:13.031 --> 01:50:16.398
- Don't move.
- Do you see anything?

01:50:18.270 --> 01:50:22.206
It's the guy. He's here.
He's got a gun to my head.

01:50:25.310 --> 01:50:26.834
Nobody moves.

01:50:26.912 --> 01:50:29.779
- Let the girl go.
- Take it easy, man!

01:50:32.251 --> 01:50:35.687
Okay, the girl's comin' out.
Let the girl go.

01:50:45.764 --> 01:50:49.063
Grab the axe off the wall.
Over there. Go!

01:50:52.404 --> 01:50:54.463
You're coming with us.

01:51:06.718 --> 01:51:08.481
Christ, he shot him!

01:51:09.922 --> 01:51:12.390
Bastard!

01:51:21.466 --> 01:51:22.899
Move!

01:51:26.939 --> 01:51:29.066
- Shut the fucking water off!
- Got it.

01:51:29.141 --> 01:51:31.268
Come!

01:51:32.411 --> 01:51:36.108
We're in a bad way here.
Send the cats.

01:51:46.225 --> 01:51:49.922
I don't know what happened.
I didn't see 'em coming, I swear!

01:51:49.995 --> 01:51:55.558
I just went shopping and I came back,
and they were everywhere.

01:51:57.336 --> 01:51:59.463
Stay away from the window.

01:52:45.851 --> 01:52:47.284
Come here.

01:52:49.755 --> 01:52:51.188
Snipers.

01:52:53.258 --> 01:52:57.160
Okay, now, get this fucking asshole
out of there.

01:53:14.880 --> 01:53:18.714
- How are we gonna get outta here now?
- Leave it to me. We're checking out.

01:54:19.244 --> 01:54:22.873
But it's not big enough for you.
It's barely big enough for me.

01:54:22.948 --> 01:54:26.748
- We said no discussion.
- No, I'm not letting...

01:54:26.818 --> 01:54:31.812
- I'm not going! I won't go!
- Listen to me.

01:54:33.325 --> 01:54:35.623
We have no chance together.
But if I'm alone, I can do it.

01:54:35.694 --> 01:54:37.924
Trust me.
I'm in good shape.

01:54:37.996 --> 01:54:40.794
I know I've got a lot of money with Tony.

01:54:40.866 --> 01:54:43.528
We'll take it and leave together,
just the two of us.

01:54:43.602 --> 01:54:45.092
Go.

01:54:45.170 --> 01:54:48.469
You're saying that so I won't worry.

01:54:52.377 --> 01:54:55.835
- I don't wanna lose you.
- You're not gonna lose me.

01:54:55.914 --> 01:54:57.848
You've given me a taste for life.

01:54:57.916 --> 01:55:01.249
I wanna be happy, sleep in a bed, have roots.

01:55:01.319 --> 01:55:03.446
You'll never be alone again.

01:55:06.792 --> 01:55:09.989
Please, go now, baby. Go.

01:55:12.063 --> 01:55:14.531
Calm down.
Go now. Go.

01:55:17.235 --> 01:55:21.228
See you at Tony's. I'm gonna
clean them all. Tony's in an hour.

01:55:26.912 --> 01:55:29.142
I love you, Mathilda.

01:55:29.214 --> 01:55:31.273
I love you, too, Leon.

01:56:06.284 --> 01:56:11.779
Hey, what is going on up there?
Take the guy out, not the building.

01:56:32.010 --> 01:56:34.137
We've got one breathing here!

01:56:36.014 --> 01:56:38.278
Get a medic on the horn!

01:56:41.720 --> 01:56:44.120
Clear the hall!
Let him through!

01:56:46.758 --> 01:56:50.558
- We've got a wounded man. Make way!
- Down those stairs.

01:56:53.698 --> 01:56:55.393
Let's go! Move!

01:56:55.467 --> 01:56:57.264
Get that guy off the stairs!

01:56:57.335 --> 01:57:00.827
- Get your team back out there!
- I got him!

01:57:00.906 --> 01:57:03.966
We've got two men comin'
down the stairs. Let's hurry!

01:57:25.730 --> 01:57:29.564
You okay?
Hey, I need a medic over here!

01:57:29.634 --> 01:57:31.659
Move your fuckin' asses.

01:57:31.736 --> 01:57:34.227
Squad Number One,
what's the status on the apartment?

01:57:34.306 --> 01:57:36.638
<i>Can't see shit. Too much smoke.
Give us five minutes.</i>

01:57:36.708 --> 01:57:38.141
You got it.

01:57:38.209 --> 01:57:41.838
What? Two hundred men can't find
one man and a girl?

01:57:41.913 --> 01:57:43.471
Did you find the girl?

01:57:52.724 --> 01:57:55.318
How are you doing?
Take your mask off, quick.

01:57:58.229 --> 01:58:02.325
Let me see you. That's deep.
Right. And this one here...

01:58:02.400 --> 01:58:05.631
You're from the 3rd Precinct?

01:58:08.106 --> 01:58:11.337
Let's open up his sleeve a little bit.

01:58:14.579 --> 01:58:17.673
All right, fine. Put it down.
This one.

01:58:34.499 --> 01:58:36.558
You stay there for two minutes.
I'll be right back.

01:58:36.635 --> 01:58:40.127
Let me put the mask back on.
I breathe better with it.

01:58:40.205 --> 01:58:44.198
You're all right.
Sit tight.

01:58:49.948 --> 01:58:55.409
Come on, everybody out!
Let's go! Out!

01:59:19.844 --> 01:59:22.972
Clear the way, men.

01:59:32.023 --> 01:59:34.389
What are you doing here?
Get out. Come on.

02:01:27.906 --> 02:01:30.033
At your service.

02:01:38.616 --> 02:01:42.575
This is from...

02:01:48.660 --> 02:01:50.924
Mathilda.

02:02:06.010 --> 02:02:07.875
Shit.

02:02:29.334 --> 02:02:30.767
Get out of here!

02:02:34.138 --> 02:02:37.005
Leon asked me to help you out...

02:02:37.075 --> 02:02:41.011
if somethin' happened,
and I think somethin' happened.

02:02:41.079 --> 02:02:44.845
He put aside a little cash for you.

02:02:44.916 --> 02:02:48.079
So what I'm suggesting is that...

02:02:48.152 --> 02:02:50.620
seein' as how you're still so young...

02:02:50.688 --> 02:02:53.623
I should hold the money for you
until you're older.

02:02:53.691 --> 02:02:55.818
Like a bank, you know, except...

02:02:55.894 --> 02:02:59.955
it's better than a bank
'cause banks always get knocked off.

02:03:00.031 --> 02:03:02.727
No one knocks off old Tony.

02:03:02.800 --> 02:03:05.462
But it's your money.
In the meantime...

02:03:05.536 --> 02:03:09.472
all you gotta do is come here
every once in awhile...

02:03:09.540 --> 02:03:13.306
and I'll dish it out
so you can have a little fun.

02:03:14.445 --> 02:03:15.878
Here.

02:03:15.947 --> 02:03:21.442
- Here's a hundred bucks to start.
- Can't I get a job instead?

02:03:21.519 --> 02:03:26.456
A job?
What the hell can you do?

02:03:26.524 --> 02:03:28.355
I can clean.

02:03:29.727 --> 02:03:32.195
I ain't got no work
for a 12-year-old kid...

02:03:32.263 --> 02:03:34.356
so get it out of your goddamn head!

02:03:34.432 --> 02:03:37.162
It's over!
The game's over!

02:03:37.235 --> 02:03:39.965
Leon's dead!

02:03:40.038 --> 02:03:42.006
You hear me?

02:03:49.213 --> 02:03:53.946
Come on. You think
I ain't hurtin' too?

02:03:59.424 --> 02:04:01.824
But he's dead.

02:04:01.893 --> 02:04:05.852
You're gonna forget all this craziness
and get your little ass back to school.

02:04:07.098 --> 02:04:10.192
Now take this money and get the hell outta here.

02:04:10.268 --> 02:04:12.361
Don't let me see your face till next month...

02:04:12.437 --> 02:04:16.703
'cause something tells me
I'm about to lose my famous kind streak.

02:05:07.959 --> 02:05:11.417
My parents...

02:05:11.496 --> 02:05:13.589
died...

02:05:13.664 --> 02:05:18.260
in a car accident four weeks ago.

02:05:18.336 --> 02:05:20.270
It was terrible.

02:05:22.840 --> 02:05:26.606
We didn't have the time to get to know
one another when you first came here...

02:05:26.677 --> 02:05:31.410
but I want you to know I'm not the kind
of woman who'd let down a child...

02:05:31.482 --> 02:05:34.815
whatever her situation, whatever her mistake.

02:05:34.886 --> 02:05:39.949
So I'm going to help you and do my best
to welcome you here again.

02:05:41.859 --> 02:05:44.521
But on one condition:

02:05:44.595 --> 02:05:47.792
You have to stop lying to me, Mathilda.

02:05:47.865 --> 02:05:50.026
I want you to take a chance...

02:05:50.101 --> 02:05:53.036
and trust me.

02:05:53.104 --> 02:05:55.629
Tell me what happened to you.

02:05:59.043 --> 02:06:02.137
My family got shot down
by D.E.A. officers...

02:06:02.213 --> 02:06:05.649
because of a drug problem.

02:06:05.716 --> 02:06:08.310
I left with the greatest guy on Earth.

02:06:08.386 --> 02:06:13.153
He was a hit man, the best in town,
but he died this morning.

02:06:13.224 --> 02:06:17.092
If you don't help me, I'll be dead by tonight.

02:06:36.481 --> 02:06:40.144
- You know her?
- I've never seen her.

02:07:06.711 --> 02:07:09.373
I think we'll be okay here.

